      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 05:01:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易还是战争？美国和伊朗之间即将开始的重要谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/26/world/middleeast/iran-us-nuclear-talks.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[特朗普总统不断发出威胁，并在该地区增兵。伊朗的任务是让他取得胜利，但同时也要保留一定程度的核浓缩能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/26/world/middleeast/iran-us-nuclear-talks.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 05:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱泼斯坦的文件中缺少有关针对特朗普提出索赔的女性的记录</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/25/us/politics/trump-epstein-files.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[司法部公布的文件简要提及一名妇女未经证实的指控，称唐纳德·J·特朗普在 20 世纪 80 年代袭击了她，当时她还是未成年人。但与她的帐户相关的几份备忘录并不在文件中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/25/us/politics/trump-epstein-files.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Feb 2026 03:04:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
